data.description: Welcome Home to 10+ acres of privacy!!  24x24 detached garage with heat and air, 2 car carport, detached shed!!  Enter the Great Room with vaulted ceilings and exposed beams with warming gas fireplace!  Eat-in Kitchen includes stove, dishwasher & refrigerator with lots of natural light.  3 oversized bedrooms and 2 full baths!  Primary bedroom is huge and includes private bath with shower and jetted tub & enormous walk-in closet!   This home also includes a 6 x 5 room perfect for office! 2 level deck ready to entertain! Whole house generator.
